  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13068934/canada-twin-centres-lp-image.jpg" alt="Canada Twin Centre" rel="879,452" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Best of Alberta skiing</h2>
<p>Enjoy the very best of Alberta skiing, superb skiing in Jasper followed by the SkiBig3 with stay in Banff.</p>
<p>Your first week will be in majestic <a data-udi="umb://document/bfa04f44790c46849e2845718190cf27" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfa04f44790c46849e2845718190cf27}" title="Jasper">Jasper</a>, skiing the Marmot Basin - the highest elevation in Canada. Followed by your second week in <a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff">Banff</a> and skiing the SkiBig3 resorts of Sunshine Village, Norquay and Lake Louise Ski area.</p>
<p>We have selected the following combinations of hotels which, in our opinion,offer similar level of quality of accommodation:</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3670ba460aa64f3d91718667e107b597" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3670ba460aa64f3d91718667e107b597}" title="Sawridge Hotel">Sawridge Hotel</a><strong> </strong>in Jasper and <a data-udi="umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a}" title="Caribou Lodge">Caribou Lodge</a> in Banff from £1,469 per person (Holiday code CAXX 3206)</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/85409848b65944fd92e7a33f52443b73" href="/{localLink:umb://document/85409848b65944fd92e7a33f52443b73}" title="Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge">Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7}" title="Fairmont Banff Springs">Fairmont Banff Springs</a> from £1,959 per person (Holiday code CAXX 3207)</p>
<p>Prices include return flights on Wednesday or Saturday, 7 nights accommodation on room only basis in each resort, all coach transfers and accommodation as advertised.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Best of Canada skiing</h2>
<p>Combine the SkiBig3 resorts with the award winning ski Whistler.</p>
<p>Your first week will be in Banff enjoying the challenge of the SkiBig3 area.Followed by your second week in <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a>, the number one ski resort in North America.</p>
<p><span>We have selected the following combinations of hotels which, in our opinion,offer similar level of quality of accommodation:</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a}" title="Caribou Lodge">Caribou Lodge</a> in Banff and <a data-udi="umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802}" title="Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites">Crystal Lodge</a> in Whistler from £1,819 per person (Holiday code CAXX 3208)</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7}" title="Fairmont Banff Springs">Banff Springs</a> in Banff and <a data-udi="umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3}" title="Fairmont Chateau Whistler">Chateau Whistler</a> in Whistler from £2,249 per person (Holiday code CAXX 3209)</p>
<p><span>Prices include return flights on Wednesday or Saturday, 7 nights accommodation on room only basis in each resort, domestic flight from Calgary to Vancouver and all coach transfers and accommodation as advertised.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 align="center">For more information or to book our Canada Two Centre Ski Holiday please call 01483 79 11 12</h3>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
